snippet.textDisplay: I have watched SNL my whole life,, I discovered when I was like 6 years old and I had no idea what I was watching but I knew I liked it!! I grew up in the years where the cast was absolutely amazing! I feel sorry for people who didn't get to watch some of the greatest years on SNL because now it has lost so many things that made it great!! This show has seriously became less and less funny,, I mean seriously, how many sketches make people actually laugh to the point of crying anymore? Yeah of course their our still some funny parts, but it seems to be pretty rare! Also they use to make their political sketches funny but now they just try and push a certain agenda!
